BT /F1 10 Tf 50 745 Td (UrbanFlow is an AI-powered adaptive traffic signal control system that uses real-time computer) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 731 Td (vision and reinforcement learning to optimize traffic flow at intersections. Unlike) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 717 Td (traditional fixed-timer traffic signals that operate on predetermined schedules, UrbanFlow) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 703 Td (dynamically adjusts signal phases based on actual traffic conditions detected through a mobile) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 689 Td (phone camera.) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 667 Td (The system consists of three core components:) Tj ET
0.23 0.51 0.96 rg
BT /F1 12 Tf 65 653 Td (·) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 79 653 Td (A mobile phone camera for real-time traffic video capture and transmission) Tj ET
0.23 0.51 0.96 rg
BT /F1 12 Tf 65 639 Td (·) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 79 639 Td (A computer vision engine for vehicle detection, counting, and signal state recognition) Tj ET
0.23 0.51 0.96 rg
BT /F1 12 Tf 65 625 Td (·) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 79 625 Td (A reinforcement learning agent \(Actor-Critic A2C\) that learns optimal signal timing) Tj ET
0.23 0.51 0.96 rg
BT /F1 12 Tf 65 611 Td (·) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 79 611 Td (A real-time dashboard for monitoring and visualization) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 589 Td (The key innovation is replacing expensive fixed infrastructure \(loop detectors, radar\) with a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 575 Td (single smartphone, making smart traffic management accessible and affordable for any) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 561 Td (intersection. Early results show a potential 30-40% reduction in average vehicle waiting time) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 547 Td (compared to fixed-timer systems.) Tj ET
endstream
