BT /F2 16 Tf 50 737 Td (2.1 The Traffic Crisis) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 715 Td (Urban traffic congestion costs the global economy over $1 trillion annually in wasted fuel,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 701 Td (lost productivity, and environmental damage. Traditional traffic management relies on) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 687 Td (fixed-timer signals that operate on preset schedules regardless of actual traffic volume.) Tj ET
0.23 0.38 0.96 rg
BT /F2 16 Tf 50 660 Td (2.2 Limitations of Current Systems) Tj ET
0.23 0.51 0.96 rg
BT /F1 12 Tf 65 638 Td (·) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 79 638 Td (Fixed timers waste green time when no vehicles are waiting) Tj ET
0.23 0.51 0.96 rg
BT /F1 12 Tf 65 624 Td (·) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 79 624 Td (Cannot adapt to real-time demand fluctuations \(accidents, events, weather\)) Tj ET
0.23 0.51 0.96 rg
BT /F1 12 Tf 65 610 Td (·) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 79 610 Td (Infrastructure-heavy solutions \(inductive loops, radar\) cost $50,000-$200,000 per) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 79 596 Td (intersection) Tj ET
0.23 0.51 0.96 rg
BT /F1 12 Tf 65 582 Td (·) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 79 582 Td (No learning capability -- same inefficiencies repeat daily) Tj ET
0.23 0.38 0.96 rg
BT /F2 16 Tf 50 555 Td (2.3 Our Solution) Tj ET
0.15 0.15 0.15 rg
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 533 Td (UrbanFlow addresses these limitations by using a smartphone camera as a low-cost sensor) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 519 Td (combined with AI that learns to optimize signal timing from real traffic patterns. The system) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 505 Td (costs effectively $0 in additional hardware \(uses existing phones\) and improves over time) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50 491 Td (through reinforcement learning.) Tj ET
endstream
